data.description: ITS A CHRISTMAS MIRACLE!! SELLERS ARE MOTIVATED!! One of the best things about this home is its location. It is situated close to many hiking and biking trails, making it perfect for outdoor enthusiasts.   4 bedroom and 3 bath home including brand-new windows, hardwood floors, solar panel.  The master bedroom has an master bathroom with heated tile floors,  family room off of the kitchen for  relaxing with family and friends by the fireplace  The kitchen is bright and open, with its modern appliances, ample counter space and cabinets, and a beautiful backsplash.      EXTRAS  New windows 2023 New floors 2021 New carpet 2021 Solar panels  New garage door 2023 Extended driveway
